      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2025-12-22T11:13:24.1858467+03:00",
      "original_text": "\"So you knew there was a schism on the station?\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2025-12-22T11:13:24.185848+03:00",
          "locale_text": "「つまり、あなたは、駅に裂け目があることを知っていたのですか？」"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "esES",
      "text": "«Entonces, ¿sabía que había un cisma en la estación?».",
      "modification_date": "2026-01-08T12:32:07.9908716+03:00",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-01-08T12:32:07.9908717+03:00",
      "original_text": "\"So you knew there was a schism on the station?\"",
      "traits": [
        {
          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2026-01-08T12:32:07.9908723+03:00",
          "locale_text": "«Entonces, ¿sabía que había un cisma en la estación?»."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "zhCN",
      "text": "“所以你早就知道星站内部有分裂？”",
      "modification_date": "2026-01-08T12:34:27.822914+03:00",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-01-08T12:34:27.8229141+03:00",
      "original_text": "\"So you knew there was a schism on the station?\"",
